Mediums are undervalued

I'm not going to claim that we intentionally had these two points in mind when we designed the tokenomics. Except for the penthouses, we knew those were gonna be sought afetr. 

It's fun to observe how token type distribution can cause so many dynamics within communities.

The supply disparity between small, medium and large apartments causes Mediums to be "undervalued"

Normally, you would think that mediums should have at least twice the price of the smalls, because they are medium-sized.

5000 smalls, 3000 mediums (instead of 2500), 1000 large

The @Worldwide_WEB3 apartment type supply distribution design is a master class in NFT marketing through tokenomic design.

The 69 Penthouses are sought-after luxury apartments, that not everyone can have. These cause high sales which draw attention.

Mediums are undervalued.
